@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "About Us";
}

<div class="hb-card mt-4">
    <div class="hb-card-header">
        <h2>@ViewData["Title"]</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="hb-card-body">
        <h4 class="text-warning mb-3">Our History</h4>
        <p>Founded in 2020 by a group of passionate sports enthusiasts and tech visionaries, Horizon Betting started as a small concept to revolutionize the way players manage their betting accounts. Recognizing the need for a robust, transparent, and user-friendly platform, we set out to build a system that prioritizes the user experience above all else.</p>
        
        <h4 class="text-warning mt-4 mb-3">Our Inspiration</h4>
        <p>We draw our inspiration from the thrill of the game and the bold aesthetics of modern sports entertainment. We believe that managing your funds should be as exciting and reliable as placing the winning bet. Our bold colors and energetic layout reflect our commitment to excellence and high performance.</p>

        <h4 class="text-warning mt-4 mb-3">How We Serve Our Clients</h4>
        <p>Horizon Betting provides a seamless interface for users to keep track of their accounts and transactions. We offer real-time updates on balances and an immutable record of all debit and credit transactions, ensuring complete transparency and trust.</p>

        <h4 class="text-warning mt-4 mb-3">What You Can Expect</h4>
        <p>When you use our platform, you can expect state-of-the-art security, zero downtime, and a beautifully crafted interface that puts your needs first. We are constantly innovating to bring you the best betting-account management experience on the market.</p>
    </div>
</div>
